Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.78,0:24:01.24,Vinland-ed2-jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}You're gonna make me go
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.78,0:24:01.24,Vinland-ed2-ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}你讓我離開
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.39,0:24:03.78,Vinland-ed2-jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}You're gonna make me drown
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.39,0:24:03.78,Vinland-ed2-ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}你使我沉淪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.05,0:24:08.65,Vinland-ed2-jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}No, I don't want it, I don't want it, I don't want it
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.05,0:24:08.65,Vinland-ed2-ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}但我不願離開  不願沉淪  不願失去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.02,0:24:11.73,Vinland-ed2-jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}But I know no one's there
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.02,0:24:11.73,Vinland-ed2-ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}但我早已知曉  那裡空無一人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.52,0:24:19.44,Vinland-ed2-jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}I will stay right here
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.52,0:24:19.44,Vinland-ed2-ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}我會佇立於此
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.65,0:24:22.28,Vinland-ed2-jp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}狭間を辿って
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.65,0:24:22.28,Vinland-ed2-ch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(300,300)}於夾縫中前行
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Vinland-text,,0,0,0,,——————ED——————
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.96,0:03:12.29,Vinland-title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1626,891)}{\fad(800,1000)\blur7}#14  晓光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.59,0:03:10.68,Vinland-tips,NTP,0,0,0,,注：《圣经旧约·耶利米哀歌》第5章第21句。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.59,0:03:10.68,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,耶和华啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.68,0:03:16.91,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,求你使我们回转归向你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.07,0:03:19.80,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就得以回转
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.20,0:03:23.61,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,求你更新我们的年日
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.16,0:03:27.60,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,像古时一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.86,0:03:37.50,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说  神父
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.23,0:03:41.74,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我想起来了  我和这位大哥就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.48,0:03:45.18,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们从小做什么事都是一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.49,0:03:47.76,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以来都互相帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.18,0:03:53.51,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,战场上的默契不输任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.91,0:03:54.52,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.90,0:03:58.15,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,说的没错  我们心灵相通
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.81,0:04:01.56,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我能托付后背的人只有他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.12,0:04:06.71,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,这种信赖用银币也换不来的吧  大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.90,0:04:08.92,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,废话  老弟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.17,0:04:10.91,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不过也得看有多少金额
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.82,0:04:15.02,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的兄弟情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.93,0:04:18.81,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.81,0:04:20.04,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,是你说的爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.97,0:04:21.97,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.58,0:04:24.23,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,到底对不对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.65,0:04:29.18,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是和我想象中的爱完全不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.74,0:04:32.99,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你啊  神父
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.02,0:04:36.35,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有上过战场
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.46,0:04:38.27,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不懂这种默契的厉害之处
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.81,0:04:41.02,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,生死之间的配合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.58,0:04:43.72,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你做得来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.78,0:04:48.19,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得这是很美好的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.65,0:04:52.92,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,对于你们兄弟来说应该是无价之宝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.16,0:04:57.95,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  假如我站上了战场
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.75,0:05:02.02,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你会保护我的后背吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.58,0:05:05.17,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.39,0:05:07.74,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我说了只有跟大哥才做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.88,0:05:10.58,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能会把后背交给一个酒鬼僧侣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.29,0:05:13.20,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也这么觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.81,0:05:14.84,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:19.86,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  你能不能说得简单一点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.23,0:05:21.49,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.63,0:05:23.21,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.58,0:05:28.07,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你那么喜欢酒  这个酒不就是爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.95,0:05:34.11,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不对  而且我并不喜欢酒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.54,0:05:35.10,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.64,0:05:36.38,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那就别喝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.06,0:05:38.15,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.50,0:05:40.23,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,这人莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.99,0:05:42.74,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,就是好在莫名其妙这一点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.07,0:05:45.20,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那你听听看这个故事怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.39,0:05:49.03,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,在老团员之间这事至今还是会被提起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.61,0:05:53.02,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们曾经在法罗群岛袭击船舶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:56.79,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那艘船上有一个战士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.35,0:06:00.19,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,他真的是太强了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.07,0:06:03.94,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们全部人都攻了上去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.17,0:06:08.84,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那人空着手一下子就把三十个人打倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.00,0:06:09.90,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,空着手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.50,0:06:14.63,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然最后他被我们干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.90,0:06:16.35,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,可是事后我们清点损失
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.52,0:06:18.44,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,发现居然没有死人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.36,0:06:21.40,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,当时到底是什么情况呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.08,0:06:24.91,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙好像背着一把剑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.15,0:06:27.89,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们应该是被小看了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.38,0:06:30.05,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是这样的话就太让人火大了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.31,0:06:32.97,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,一点作为战士的礼貌都…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.99,0:06:39.91,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人还做了什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:42.32,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,名字叫什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.58,0:06:45.16,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,名字不记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.10,0:06:52.00,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,莫名其妙的人之间果然是臭味相投的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.37,0:06:54.91,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个家伙也说了些奇怪的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.49,0:07:00.44,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,「真正的战士不需要剑」来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.97,0:07:12.41,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  怎么了  僧侣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.13,0:07:14.84,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,等…你要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.99,0:07:21.70,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,僧侣  你到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.97,0:07:23.59,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的说对了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.70,0:07:24.53,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,是爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.78,0:07:38.10,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,战士…真正的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.81,0:07:40.78,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要剑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.82,0:07:50.84,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的…战士…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.94,0:08:06.49,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟我说也没用  要怪就怪这天气
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.11,0:08:08.92,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我是个船员
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.17,0:08:10.33,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,海上还好说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.71,0:08:13.50,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,陆地的天气我可不好预测
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.09,0:08:18.82,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,更不可能预料到刚入冬就积了那么厚的雪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.71,0:08:21.69,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.89,0:08:26.42,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说你的时运没那么好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:28.92,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,遇到雪天就急着改变行进路线
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.92,0:08:30.00,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,结果一下成这样子了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.61,0:08:33.68,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你的很多士兵都已经开始动摇了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.82,0:08:38.07,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我的手下都有过无数次出生入死的经历
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.23,0:08:41.11,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,这种程度的天气才不会怕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.61,0:08:44.53,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,他们不都在麻利地听从命令行进着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.18,0:08:49.26,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,返回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.62,0:08:51.46,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,横跨麦西亚是不可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.56,0:08:57.62,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,拨开雪前进的话就得丢掉战利品
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.86,0:08:59.83,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,手下们怕是不愿意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.82,0:09:01.59,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.30,0:09:04.29,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚已经没办法露营了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.52,0:09:08.37,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,阿谢拉特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.85,0:09:10.08,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.57,0:09:11.42,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,可以开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.33,0:09:12.85,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.10,0:09:16.02,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,阿谢拉特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.44,0:09:21.88,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,没有时运的时候  做什么都不会如意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.93,0:09:23.02,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,朗纳尔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.15,0:09:27.82,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么要这么犹豫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.08,0:09:33.98,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,袭击  掠夺村落
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.14,0:09:37.85,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我们诺尔斯人的传统吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.54,0:09:48.09,Vinland-tips,NTP,0,0,0,,注：语出《圣经新约·马太福音》第6章第11-13句，讲述耶稣教导信众如何祷告的情节。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.54,0:09:48.09,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在天上的父
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:52.18,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我们日用的饮食  今日赐给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.78,0:09:57.92,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,免我们的债  如同我们免了人的债
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.74,0:10:02.35,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不叫我们陷入试探  救我们脱离那恶者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.19,0:10:05.05,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为国度  权柄  荣耀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.35,0:10:07.70,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,全是你的  直到永远
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.59,0:10:09.06,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,阿门
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.73,0:10:10.85,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,阿门
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.46,0:10:18.70,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.24,0:10:21.81,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么总是要祈祷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.30,0:10:26.20,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为耶稣要让我们这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.09,0:10:29.09,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,耶稣说的话不会有错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.71,0:10:31.83,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不祈祷会发生什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.64,0:10:33.75,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,这还用问
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.00,0:10:37.01,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不相信他的人死后就会落入地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.32,0:10:38.22,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.68,0:10:42.93,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,地狱很可怕  里头全是恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.03,0:10:44.78,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,恶魔很可怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.57,0:10:48.20,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我害怕恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:50.07,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸也害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.80,0:10:54.58,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是会祈祷的好孩子能去天堂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.78,0:10:56.20,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,好好记住了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.73,0:11:01.49,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是没什么实感
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.25,0:11:06.06,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不久以后大家就要被带到天堂或者地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.67,0:11:09.60,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不想一家人都被迫分开
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.45,0:11:11.75,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  爸爸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.21,0:11:16.34,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么神突然决定要审判这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:17.92,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,这不突然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.35,0:11:20.43,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,他很早以前就决定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.84,0:11:24.39,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,就定在耶稣复活一千年后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.76,0:11:27.49,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是二十年后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.84,0:11:24.39,Vinland-tips,NTP,0,0,0,,注：末日审判的其中一种预言假说，当时一些基督徒宣称，\N世界末日将在耶稣死后复活一千年（1033年）降临。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.26,0:11:35.66,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,神会降下审判
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.86,0:11:38.06,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,坏人全都将下地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.00,0:11:39.98,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.38,0:11:42.05,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,坏人就是丹麦人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.32,0:11:44.41,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  他们超级坏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.92,0:11:50.29,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,神一定知道会有那样的人出现
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.72,0:11:51.39,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.85,0:11:55.20,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你们要好好听耶稣的教诲…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.29,0:11:56.78,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.66,0:12:00.95,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我去小便
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.63,0:12:11.44,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办  怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.79,0:12:13.67,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我好害怕恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.66,0:12:37.16,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是好美
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.76,0:12:40.23,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,又戴上了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.78,0:12:44.00,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,这个戒指要花多少钱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.79,0:12:49.25,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,现在付钱的话  神还会原谅我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.01,0:12:57.48,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那肯定是来自恶魔的诱惑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.97,0:13:05.33,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,明明连钱都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.52,0:13:08.23,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,就不该去逛集市的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.13,0:13:12.92,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,像我这样的坏孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.51,0:13:16.62,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定会在审判之日下地狱的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.14,0:13:22.17,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,家里肯定只有我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.47,0:13:25.21,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,无法去天国
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.54,0:13:44.38,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,戴在左手也真好看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.54,0:13:52.30,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.56,0:13:58.99,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那张脸算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.20,0:14:02.59,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会  我也会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.10,0:14:06.49,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚的话没听到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.80,0:14:08.37,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不好好做个好孩子的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.55,0:14:10.02,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,神会惩罚…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.16,0:14:17.51,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.98,0:14:19.85,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,找到晚饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.96,0:14:25.93,Vinland-picture - v2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\frz270\pos(1248,246)}你竟全然抛弃我们，\N向我们大发雷霆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.96,0:14:25.93,Vinland-tips,NTP,0,0,0,,《圣经旧约·耶利米哀歌》第5章第22节。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.63,0:14:32.56,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,大家  快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.00,0:14:35.06,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,这个村子已经被盯上了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.16,0:14:37.86,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,丹麦人  要将这个村子…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.86,0:14:39.66,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,别嚷嚷你个臭僧侣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.01,0:14:41.02,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你想死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.27,0:14:50.61,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,真暖和  活过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.61,0:14:51.69,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,这一家是什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.96,0:14:53.18,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,好多小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.23,0:14:56.93,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你们是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.93,0:14:57.46,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,突然就…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.38,0:15:01.55,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,大麦  牛奶粥和一点肉干
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.42,0:15:03.75,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,放了洋葱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.74,0:15:07.42,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,把能当武器的东西都收起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.53,0:15:07.92,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.73,0:15:17.45,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,难吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.71,0:15:19.76,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,真亏你们吃得下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.42,0:15:24.53,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你是在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.05,0:15:28.13,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,浪费粮食会遭天谴…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.52,0:15:27.32,Vinland-text - top,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.25,0:15:35.88,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.27,0:15:40.53,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那啥  用英格兰语怎么说的来着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.28,0:15:42.87,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,交出所有吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.75,0:15:44.54,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,对对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.68,0:15:47.19,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.32,0:15:47.70,Vinland-text - top,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.66,0:15:48.26,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,看这边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.96,0:15:55.24,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,交出所有吃的  不然杀光你们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.83,0:16:01.43,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,是这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.43,0:16:06.27,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,只有这些吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.79,0:16:12.55,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,2个小孩算1个人  就一共有50人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.72,0:16:15.85,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说越冬的储粮也差不多是50人的量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.84,0:16:24.18,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,对104名战士来说有点不够啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.99,0:16:29.38,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办  怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.17,0:16:31.96,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都被抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.10,0:16:32.91,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.17,0:16:38.25,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,神父啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.74,0:16:43.19,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你是王子的教师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.34,0:16:45.62,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,也算是这个兵团的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.99,0:16:48.20,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,只原谅你一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.60,0:16:50.60,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果下次还碍事的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.94,0:16:52.27,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,当场就把你杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.78,0:16:56.16,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我本来就讨厌僧侣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.29,0:17:00.88,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.57,0:17:03.56,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,是丹麦人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.53,0:17:07.23,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,有通晓我们语言的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.30,0:17:16.84,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.45,0:17:18.64,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,能把一半食物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.34,0:17:21.44,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,至少能给我们留下一半吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.25,0:17:23.19,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,有一半食物的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.52,0:17:25.16,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,冬天就能想办法熬过了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.00,0:17:30.25,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,村里还有婴儿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.88,0:17:31.63,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,还请大发慈悲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.70,0:17:35.10,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,婴儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.33,0:17:36.70,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那也挺辛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.13,0:17:41.06,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.39,0:17:43.72,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的事情已经考虑过了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.32,0:17:46.86,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不用担心越冬的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.68,0:17:50.72,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的  真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.37,0:17:52.53,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.34,0:17:54.96,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,无论明年还是后年
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.05,0:17:57.21,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,都不用担心越冬了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.60,0:18:01.48,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,让你们从苦恼中解脱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.05,0:18:10.81,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,阿谢拉特  他们都是非战斗人员
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.16,0:18:15.88,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,让他们活着也没有给他们吃的饭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.75,0:18:18.45,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕是逃走了一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.54,0:18:21.48,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,就有可能暴露我们还在敌人腹地磨蹭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.59,0:18:23.11,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那可是万万受不起的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.62,0:18:26.87,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,如何  坑挖好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.04,0:18:27.86,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.96,0:18:29.89,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,挤一挤可以容得下六十人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.83,0:18:34.77,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,阿谢拉特  这些人是基督教徒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.55,0:18:36.99,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.69,0:18:41.15,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是保护王子最好的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.71,0:18:44.30,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那么其他人有问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.64,0:18:46.73,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,看来没有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.35,0:18:47.91,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.58,0:18:49.75,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那么弟兄们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.72,0:18:53.46,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,动手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.94,0:20:41.21,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.93,0:20:47.58,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,您看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.34,0:21:00.63,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸  妈妈  爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.43,0:21:03.18,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,还有弟弟和妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.68,0:21:10.08,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,已经到您身边去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.93,0:21:29.26,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,您果然不喜欢我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.47,0:21:34.48,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢  因为我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.64,0:21:39.93,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,怦然心动了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.14,0:21:52.14,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,居然有  居然有如此坏的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.09,0:21:58.43,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,居然有这么多人不惧怕您的惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.23,0:22:05.44,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,就如同偷走戒指时的那一瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.45,0:22:09.06,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.91,0:22:14.94,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,怦然心动了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,——ED——
